=================================================
FS25 Seasons Animals
Architecture
=================================================

Project Philosophy
-------------------------------------------------

Create the most realistic and enjoyable cattle
experience possible while remaining:

- Lightweight
- Modular
- Transparent
- XML-driven
- Removable without destroying saves

The core mod should provide a complete cattle
experience by itself.

Future systems should be implemented as optional
submods.

-------------------------------------------------
Version 1 Scope
-------------------------------------------------

Supported Species

- Dairy Cattle
- Beef Cattle

Not Supported

- Sheep
- Goats
- Pigs
- Horses
- Buffalo
- Chickens

-------------------------------------------------
Core Systems
-------------------------------------------------

Weight

- Daily weight gain
- Weight affects sale price
- Weight affects feed consumption

Reproduction

- 21 day estrus cycle
- ±5 day variation
- AI breeding only
- 5% conception failure
- Male and female calves

Lactation

- Natural lactation cycle
- Dry periods

Health

- 100% maximum
- XML configurable minimum
- Overcrowding penalties
- Equal damage and recovery rates

Pricing

Final price affected by:

- Weight
- Health
- Genetics

-------------------------------------------------
Health Philosophy
-------------------------------------------------

Never destroy animals.

Poor management should reduce profits, not erase
progress.

No:

- Random deaths
- Diseases
- Heat stress
- Veterinary systems

unless players have tools to manage them.

-------------------------------------------------
Housing
-------------------------------------------------

Over-capacity births are allowed.

Newborn calves are never deleted.

After a grace period:

- Health decreases

Consequences:

Dairy:
- Reduced milk production

Beef:
- Reduced weight gain

Health affects sale price.

-------------------------------------------------
Genetics
-------------------------------------------------

Version 1

STANDARD

PREMIUM

Premium advantages:

- Higher mature weights
- Better milk production

Premium disadvantages:

- Higher feed consumption
- Lower conception rate

Tradeoffs are required.

-------------------------------------------------
Savegame Philosophy
-------------------------------------------------

All custom data stored in:

savegame#/seasonsAnimals.xml

Removing the mod should not destroy animals.

Reinstalling the mod should restore all data.

-------------------------------------------------
Existing Save Support
-------------------------------------------------

The mod must work with existing saves.

Vanilla animals should be converted automatically.

Initial values:

Health = 100%

Genetics = STANDARD

Reproduction State = OPEN

Weight calculated from age.

-------------------------------------------------
Update Philosophy
-------------------------------------------------

Most calculations occur once per day.

Temporary lag during daily updates is acceptable.

Simulation accuracy preferred over constant CPU use.

-------------------------------------------------
Submod Philosophy
-------------------------------------------------

Species are plugins.

Core framework remains universal.

Future species:

- Sheep
- Goats
- Pigs

should exist as independent submods.

